bench to lead the  Dallas Mavericks  to a 105-95 win against the
 Miami Heat  and the first National Basketball Association
championship in franchise history.  Dirk Nowitzki , who finally got an  NBA championship  ring in
his 13th season with the Mavericks, added 21 points as  Dallas 
won the series four games to two.  LeBron James  had 21 points for Miami, and committed six of
